  "title": "3 Months Temp Medical Technologist (Chemistry bench) #HAL",
  "description": "<p><strong>Location:</strong> Aljunied <br /><strong>Salary:</strong> $18.40 per hour (No CPF) <br /><br /><strong>Working Hours:</strong> <br />2 rotating shifts<br />• 8. 30 am to 5.00 pm <br />• 1.00 pm to 9.00 pm.<br /><br /><strong>Job Description:</strong> <br />● Responsible to perform, depending on the section posted, a variety of test procedures according to the standards set in the Laboratory with little direct supervision by a senior staff<br />● Routine sample processing such as spinning and aliquoting of patient samples.<br />● Routine qualitative and quantitative chemical analyses on blood, CSF (cerebrospinal fluid), urine and other body fluids.<br />● Routine chemistry procedures including, microscopy (urine, dysmorphic RBCs) and serology (dengue, influenza covid combo test, urine preg)<br />● Minor equipment testing (iSTAT, glucometer, hemochron, urine dipstick)<br />● Minor equipment validation (Timer, pipette, thermometer).<br />● Administrative section - responsible to perform registration of patient samples, handling telephone inquiries by clients and printing and faxing of patient results. Result retrieval and record/specimen keeping.<br /><br /><strong>Requirement:</strong> <br />● Min Bachelor Degree in Biomedical Science<br />● Min 1 month Lab experience<br />● Mandatory vaccinations are up to date ( Covid 3 jabs, MMR , Tdap, Varicella and Hep B) <br /><br /><br /><br /><br /><br />Interested candidate, kindly send a copy of your resume to <a href=\"mailto:adelinelim@recruitexpress.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>adelinelim@recruitexpress.com.sg</strong></a><strong> </strong><br /><br /><br /><br />Adeline Lim Xin Ying [R23112000]<br /><br /><br /><br />Email Address: <a href=\"mailto:adelinelim@recruitexpress.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">adelinelim@recruitexpress.com.sg</a><br /><br />Recruit Express Pte Ltd<br /><br />EA Licence No: 99C4599</p>",
